### GitHub Project View API Tests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@projectId = YOUR_PROJECT_ID_HERE

### 1. 获取项目的视图列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/github/projects/{{projectId}}/views
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. 获取项目的视图列表（带分页）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/github/projects/{{projectId}}/views?first=10&after=cursor_here
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. 根据ID获取项目视图详情
@viewId = YOUR_VIEW_ID_HERE
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/github/projects/{{projectId}}/views/{{viewId}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 4. 创建新的项目视图（表格布局）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/github/projects/{{projectId}}/views
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "My New Table View",
    "layout": "TABLE"
}

### 5. 创建新的项目视图（看板布局）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/github/projects/{{projectId}}/views
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Development Kanban",
    "layout": "BOARD"
}

### 6. 创建新的项目视图（路线图布局）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/github/projects/{{projectId}}/views
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Project Roadmap",
    "layout": "ROADMAP"
}

### 7. 更新项目视图（仅名称）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/github/projects/{{projectId}}/views/{{viewId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Updated View Name"
}

### 8. 更新项目视图（完整更新）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/github/projects/{{projectId}}/views/{{viewId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Comprehensive Task View",
    "layout": "TABLE"
}

### 9. 复制项目视图
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/github/projects/{{projectId}}/views/{{viewId}}/copy
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "newName": "Copy of Original View"
}

### 10. 删除项目视图
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/github/projects/{{projectId}}/views/{{viewId}}

### 测试错误情况

### 11. 获取不存在的项目视图
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/github/projects/{{projectId}}/views/invalid-view-id
Content-Type: application/json

### 12. 创建视图时缺少必需字段
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/github/projects/{{projectId}}/views
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "layout": "TABLE"
}

### 13. 更新不存在的视图
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/github/projects/{{projectId}}/views/invalid-view-id
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "This will fail"
}

### 14. 删除不存在的视图
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/github/projects/{{projectId}}/views/invalid-view-id

### 使用说明
# 1. 请将 YOUR_PROJECT_ID_HERE 替换为实际的 GitHub 项目 ID
# 2. 请将 YOUR_VIEW_ID_HERE 替换为实际的视图 ID
# 3. 确保 GitHub Access Token 在 appsettings.json 中正确配置
# 4. 确保 Token 具有适当的权限来管理项目视图

### 获取项目 ID 的辅助请求
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/github/projects
Content-Type: application/json

### 获取用户信息（用于调试）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/github/user-info
Content-Type: application/json
